{
  "stem": "15577.3",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We have to serve-- we had to serve them.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And you had to control the, the, the water, to make it warm enough or cold enough or how they want it.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they want it-- they want it it's always otherwise than you did it.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And by the time they didn't get what you wanted, they beat you.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So, it was-- But, in general, it was a very-- it was a good place, in-- if you-- the alternatives were much, much worse.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, I was infected, and I got black fever, or fleck fever.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I was taken to the hospital.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But, after a while, the doctors knew that if the Germans will know that I am infected by, by fleck fever, I have to be shot immediately, because they were so afraid of epidemic that they were always looking after it.",
      "word_count": 41
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Owing to my cousin, who was one of the doctors of the-- I was kept there as somebody who has-- I don't remember what.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Something internal.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And they didn't know.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But I was unconscious for 10 days.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But came through.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I went-- sure.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Now, then, you are-- you can work already without any fear.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You can't get twice the same.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I don't know if I am-- I was afraid.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You know, you have to know that with the time, we-- we got only used to be in danger every day, every minute, every hour, every night.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We were-- it's a hard word to say we got used to it, but we are not surprised if, in the morning, all of the camp had to stand-- Oh, by the way, all of the camp had to stand on so-called appellplatz.",
      "word_count": 43
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It means on the place where people were gathering before going to the work.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they counted everybody.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
